<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font face="Arial" size="6" color="#000080"><br>
&nbsp;COM Features</font><font color="#000080">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
</font></p>
<div v:shape="_x0000_s3074" class="O">
  <div style="mso-line-spacing: 90 30 0; mso-margin-left-alt: 348; width: 858; height: 27">
    <ul>
      <li><font color="#000080"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; text-shadow: auto; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN"><font size="5">&nbsp;&nbsp; 
        Defines a binary standard for component interoperability</font></span></font></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div style="mso-line-spacing:&quot;90 30 0&quot;;mso-margin-left-alt:348">
    <ul>
      <li><font size="5" color="#000080"><span style="text-shadow: auto">&nbsp; <span style="font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN" lang="EN-US">Is 
        programming language-independent</span></span></font></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div style="mso-line-spacing:&quot;90 30 0&quot;;mso-margin-left-alt:348">
    <ul>
      <li><font size="5" color="#000080"><span style="text-shadow: auto">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; text-shadow: auto; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN" lang="EN-US">Is 
        provided on multiple platforms (Microsoft Windows, Microsoft WindowsNT<br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Apple Macintosh, UNIX)</span></font></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div style="mso-line-spacing:&quot;90 30 0&quot;;mso-margin-left-alt:348">
    <ul>
      <li><font size="5" color="#000080"><span style="text-shadow: auto">&nbsp; <span style="font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN" lang="EN-US">Provides 
        for robust evolution of component-based applications and systems</span></span></font></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div style="mso-line-spacing:&quot;90 30 0&quot;;mso-margin-left-alt:348">
    <ul>
      <li><font size="5" color="#000080"><span style="text-shadow: auto">&nbsp; <span style="font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN" lang="EN-US">Is 
        extensible</span></span></font></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div style="mso-line-spacing:&quot;90 30 0&quot;;mso-margin-left-alt:348">
    <br>
    &nbsp;<font color="#000080" face="Arial" size="6">In addition, COM provides 
    mechanisms for the following:</font>
    <ul>
      <li><font size="5" color="#000080"><span style="text-shadow: auto">&nbsp; <span style="font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN" lang="EN-US">Communications 
        between components, even across process and network<br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; boundaries</span></span></font></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div style="mso-line-spacing:&quot;90 30 0&quot;;mso-margin-left-alt:348">
    <ul>
      <li><font size="5" color="#000080"><span style="text-shadow: auto">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; text-shadow: auto; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN" lang="EN-US">Shared 
        memory management between components</span></font></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div style="mso-line-spacing:&quot;100 50 0&quot;;mso-margin-left-alt:348">
    <ul>
      <li><font size="5" color="#000080"><span style="text-shadow: auto">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; text-shadow: auto; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN" lang="EN-US">Error 
